{
  "stem": "19921.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 308.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The Russian did very bad things with him after the-- when they took over that territory, and they didn't like the Russians.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they find out that we are from Poland, and we are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they found out also that we don't like to eat pigs, so that was fine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had to grow pigs, but we had to take care of the pigs, so.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When they saw a pig on this side of the street, they cross over.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were worse even than us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they had to grow pigs because the government asked them to.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had to have a quota of each animal to be grown-- pigs, and sheeps, and, of course, horses.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Horses they needed for one reason.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the horses-- they use the horses for the cavalry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Those are special horses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, if one of those people got recruited to the army, OK, he went along with that horse.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He got the horse from the-- from the-- from the-- place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He got the uniform and the horse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the gun he got when he entered the army, but the horse went along with him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were very good horsemen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in any event, we were working there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as far as quarters, as I mentioned, we didn't get any special houses, something like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because we were from Poland, and because we were Jewish, the-- the manager of that farm give us their office space.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, he took part of his office, and he gave us a room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, you know, provided with a kitchen or something like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember how we cooked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or we cooked outside or something like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in any event, we get a room to sleep.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
